{
  "texts": [
    "To assess the impact of frequent food delivery consumption on the long-term health of young adults in Shanghai, and",
    "To explore strategies to promote healthier food delivery options and encourage balanced eating habits among young adults in Shanghai.",
    "These objectives are achieved by providing answers to the following questions:",
    "What do young adults in Shanghai consume in their food delivery meal diets?",
    "How are food intakes and eating habits among young adults who frequently use online food delivery in Shanghai different?"
  ]
}